What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Organic Chocolate and Confectionery Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Organic Chocolate and Confectionery Market

Organic chocolate and confectionery market is expected to gain market growth in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research analyses the market to reach at an estimated value of USD 1.6 billion by 2028 and grow at a CAGR of 3.50% in the above-mentioned forecast period. Rise in the demand for organic products among population acts as an essential factor driving the organic chocolate and confectionery market.

Organic chocolate is defined as a type of chocolate that has been certified organic. Organic chocolate is a socially-desirable product for some consumers and the major brands, such as The Hershey Company, have begun to produce organic chocolate.

Rise in the health concern among diabetic patients acts as a vital factor escalating the market growth, also rise in the number of population concerned regarding their health, rise in the awareness regarding the benefits of organic products and rise in the research and development activities are the major factors among others driving the organic chocolate and confectionery market. Moreover, increase in the modernization in the new products offered in the market and rise in the demand for emerging economies will further create new opportunities for the organic chocolate and confectionery market in the forecast period of 2021- 2028.

However, rise in the cost of research and development activities and increase in the prices of organic products are the major factors among others acting as restraints, and will further challenge the organic chocolate and confectionery market in the forecast period.

